<h1>Grinnell Textbook Lending Library</h1>

<div class="infoBlock">
  <p>Welcome to the Grinnell Lending Library!</p>
  <p><font size=5>THIS IS IN PROGRESS. It does not represent the contents of
      the Grinnell Textbook Lending Library. Any similarities to books living
      or dead are purely coincidental.</font></p>
